      • processRecords

        public java.util.List processRecords(org.json.simple.JSONObject object,
                            java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> elements)
        Checks if an object exists. If exists, sets operation type to UPDATE otherwise to ADD. Checks if elements of object exists. If an element exists, replace element and element set values with the appropriate values received from Omeka. if an element does not exist, through an error for that particular element.
        Parameters:
        object - object information
        elements - set of element id and element set id
        Returns:
        Type of the operation to be performed (ADD or UPDATE) and modified object
